des: A verbal search companion to our A.I and blockchain driven platform. Easily search for stories you want to read or contribute to by saying "Alexa, open story data and search stories". After answering a few questions, Alexa will return up to five stories, from great writers, that match you answered criteria. You can search for a specific story by saying "Alexa open story data and search title {Say Title}".
